The tv was older, did not have many channels at all, mainly a news channel, tbs, a few others, No HBO or premium channels.	Centrally located right off "the main strip," The Stone Castle offers convenience, luxury, and a cozy atmosphere for the entire family.	This is definitely not a luxury hotel, but for the price, it's a great deal.	The bedding was very nice (large throw pillows and upscale comforters).	I recommend it, just don't expect luxury - expect average and clean.	Overall, we couldn't beat the price for the location and helpfulness of the staff, but I expect our rooms to be cleaner and everything well-stocked & in working order.